description: English-only rules for comments, docs, and user-facing text
globs: {R/*.R,README.md,INSTALL.md,MIGRATION_NOTES.md,tests/**/*,vignettes/**/*}
alwaysApply: false
---

# English Only

- Write all comments, roxygen docs, messages, warnings, errors, README text, INSTALL notes, migration notes, tests, and vignettes in English.
- Do not leave mixed Chinese and English text in the formal package.
- Keep terminology consistent across code and docs.
- When translating or refactoring, preserve the statistical meaning of the original implementation.
- If function names change, update all examples and documentation in the same phase.
